Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:33.97,ED7,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HBD74EB&\3c&HFFFFFF&}接下来是桂马喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:38.20,ED7,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3A48DE&}啪的左跳右跳
